==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Denigrate
<hw>Den"i*grate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>denigrare</ets>; <ets>de-</ets> + <ets>nigrare</ets> to blacken,
<ets>niger</ets> black.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To blacken thoroughly;
to make very black.</def> <rj><au>Boyle.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fig.: To blacken or sully; to defame.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To <qex>denigrate</qex> the memory of
<person>Voltaire</person>.</q> <rj><qau>Morley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>denigrating</ent>⟦br⟧
